dct_description_sm: 3 sheets joined. Wood block print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the left. Includes distance chart. Title from envelope. Publication date on envelope: "mukan'nen tadashi Tenpô ikô." Relief shown pictorially. Extension pasted on bottom of map. 1 map: col.; 84 x 46 cm., in envelope 29 x 22 cm.
